Under the effect of this spell, the caster can change at will the color of skin and hair. There is no limit to the number of changes he can perform for the duration of the spell.~
@20421 = ~To change the colors of the caster, get into his infos, click the "customize" button and then the button "color", and change colors as you wish. You can repeat it at will, and the good news is that you can even do it again after the end of the spell.~

@2051 = ~Spooky Wall~
